flowchart TD
    A[Input: User Preferences<br/>favorite_genre, favorite_mood,<br/>target_energy, likes_acoustic] --> B[Load Songs from CSV<br/>load_songs]

    B --> C{Loop: For each song<br/>in songs list}

    C --> D[score_song<br/>compare song vs user_prefs]

    D --> D1[+2.0 if genre matches]
    D --> D2[+1.0 if mood matches]
    D --> D3["+up to 1.0 for energy closeness<br/>1 - abs(song.energy - target_energy)"]
    D --> D4[+0.5 if likes_acoustic and<br/>song.acousticness > 0.6]

    D1 --> E[Accumulate score + reasons]
    D2 --> E
    D3 --> E
    D4 --> E

    E --> F["Tuple: song, score, reasons"]
    F --> C

    C -->|all songs scored| G[Sort all songs<br/>by score, descending]

    G --> H[Take Top K]

    H --> I[Output: Ranked Recommendations<br/>song, score, explanation]
